[
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Bea, need you in by 2:45 if you can. Diego bailed on Valentina's pickup, her practice ends at 3:30 en Brickell — I can't miss it if I'm doing the AM.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ugh típico. I can swing it, but the Delacroix suite folio still has two unresolved incidentals from Tuesday — did you flag those?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000001",
    "user_id": "U002BEATRI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Already escalated to Marcos. He's handling it. Just need you here before I lose the window on I-95.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "ok ok. You eating lunch before you leave? I'm grabbing cubanos from the spot on Brickell, putting in an order now",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000003",
    "user_id": "U002BEATRI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Sí, please. Add a cortadito — I've been on since 6. You're a saint, te lo juro.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "lol you say that every AM shift 😂 okay ordered. You owe me wine night details btw, Camila said something happened??",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000005",
    "user_id": "U002BEATRI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Nada que no pueda esperar. She just showed up con una botella de Malbec and three hours of opinions. Classic Camila.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "honestly I need that energy. See you in a bit — I'll take the Delacroix check-in too so you can walk out clean.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769304863.000007",
    "user_id": "U002BEATRI"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Liz — Hartwell party just pushed their arrival to 7:30pm. Presidential suite, full board. Can you stay for the check-in?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Puedo quedarme hasta 7:45, no más. Vale's volleyball is in Brickell and Diego's in Orlando so pickup is on me tonight.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000001",
    "user_id": "U003JAMES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "That's tight. Hartwell complained last trip about feeling rushed on arrival.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Give me the folio now and it won't be tight. I'll have the Biscayne itinerary and the Billecart ready before they hit the lobby.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000003",
    "user_id": "U003JAMES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Is the suite actually prepped this time? Last Thursday was a disaster.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Housekeeping confirmed at 4. I already checked the terrace myself. We're good.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000005",
    "user_id": "U003JAMES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Alright. Marco can close out after you hand off?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Sí, already texted him. Go.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769193242.000007",
    "user_id": "U003JAMES"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Marco, necesito confirmar — the Cristal for suite 1204 lands tomorrow before 2pm, sí? VIP check-in is 3 and I am not scrambling.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Confirmed, delivery window is 11–1. Two bottles as ordered plus the Bordeaux for the welcome basket. All set.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000001",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Perfecto. Make sure the driver checks in at the service entrance with Dario, not the lobby. Last time that cost me twenty minutes.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Got it, flagged on the file. Service entrance, ask for Dario. Anything else on that room?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000003",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "While I have you — Camila and I have wine night Friday, add a Malbec and a Sancerre to my personal tab. I'll grab them Thursday before shift.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Easy. The Catena Zapata just came in, and I have a Loire Sancerre she'll like. I'll pull both aside.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000005",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Sí, eso. Text me when it's ready. Gracias, Marco.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Will do. Tell Camila I said hi 😄",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769289496.000007",
    "user_id": "U004MARCO"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Shirley, AM shift runs til 3 right? Valen's volleyball pickup is 3:30 at Westchester — if the Morales group checks in late again I'm done. Did they confirm ETA?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000000",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Last I heard concierge got a 4pm ETA from the Morales rep. I can cover their greeting if you need to bounce by 3:15?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000001",
    "user_id": "U005SHIRLE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Sí, hazlo. Tell Marcos I'll take his Sunday turndown trade if he backs you up on it. Valentina's been waiting on me since Tuesday's game, no puedo fallarle.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000002",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Done. Also heads up — suite 812 called twice about Zuma reservations. Bumped it to your queue, figured you'd want that one personally.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000003",
    "user_id": "U005SHIRLE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Good call, that's the Whitfield account. They did Zuma last March, same corner table by the window. I'll pull the folio before I leave, already know what they want.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000004",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "You always know 😂 Is Camila's wine night still on or did that move?",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000005",
    "user_id": "U005SHIRLE"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
    "text": "Still on. Her place in Brickell, 8pm. She told me to bring whoever — you're welcome if you can get out. Needed after this week.",
    "thread_ts": null,
    "ts": "1769291811.000006",
    "user_id": "U001PERSONA"
  },
  {
    "channel_id": "C001GENERA",
    "reactions": "",
    "reply_count": "0",
